Script Query:

```sql
UPDATE  
  ap_metrichistory
SET
  dthreferenciainicial = TO_DATE(CONCAT(TO_CHAR(dthreferenciainicial, 'yyyy-mm-dd'), ' 00:00:00'), 'yyyy-mm-dd hh24:mi:ss'),
  dthreferenciafinal = TO_DATE(CONCAT(TO_CHAR(dthreferenciafinal, 'yyyy-mm-dd'), ' 00:00:00'), 'yyyy-mm-dd hh24:mi:ss'),
  eventtime = TO_DATE(CONCAT(TO_CHAR(eventtime, 'yyyy-mm-dd'), ' 00:00:00'), 'yyyy-mm-dd hh24:mi:ss')
WHERE 
  (TO_CHAR(dthreferenciainicial, 'hh24') != '00' OR 
  TO_CHAR(dthreferenciafinal, 'hh24') != '00' OR 
  TO_CHAR(eventtime, 'hh24') != '00') AND 
  eventtime BETWEEN to_date('[Param.1]', 'yyyy-mm-dd hh24:mi:ss') AND to_date('[Param.2]', 'yyyy-mm-dd hh24:mi:ss')

```
